You can see Harry and a Piece of Candy.
You can go south.
You are in the kitchen of Scary Godmother's house. It's cozy and tame with a strong scent of candy! In the corner you can see a werewolf rummaging about for scraps--on his blue pajama shirt is a Wal-Mart tag reading, "Hello, my Name is Harry--I really wish I wasn't here right now." You guess that the last part was added in as it looked to have been written in crayon.

