You can go southeast or north.
You stand on a dusty trail. It only drags on for a short while with the the edge of the graveyard on one side and a small, well lit building on the other side. Beside the trail is a cliff leading down into darkness. Along the entire path, the awesome structure that is Jimmy's Tower shadows the way.

