Inside the bar is the balding bartender and his patrons--a man in a '42' jersery, an adventurous woman dressed in blue, a slender scholar, and away in the corner a drunken marine.

The bartender looks at you with a smug grin, "Ah, come on in. Sorry if you had trouble up front. I don't like cheapskates just sitting around and not paying. Here, you already covered your first round." The bartender places a jar of milk on the bar for you to take and returns to his duties.
