You are in a Haunted Forest.
You can see a Corpse.
You can go south or west.
Ghosts swirl up in the air and howl solemnly. Dark trees twist together and look down at you with scary faces. Where the forest opens up you can see the start of a stone bridge.

A crack of thunder erupts. You feel you are getting close to the entrance of Jimmy's Tower.
> x corpse

> x corpse
A body, drenched in blood, lies mangled on the ground. A young black man with a red hat--his flesh looks to be rotted. He's been gone for a while now.
> w

